Class RemindersListActivity

java.lang.Object
  ListActivity
      cmput301W12.android.project.view.RemindersListActivity
All Implemented Interfaces:
FView<DatabaseModel>
public class RemindersListActivity
extends ListActivity
implements FView<DatabaseModel>

RemindersListActivity inherits ListActivity, and is responsible for updating a listview with all the alarms queried from the alarm table in the database. Each item in the list shows the text for an alarm, timestamp and alarm_type.
